===理性选择、决策论和博弈论===
{{main|博弈论}}
[[决策论|决策论]]中的哲学方法侧重于决策理论中的基本概念——例如，关于[[选择|选择]]或[[偏好|偏好]]、[[理性|理性]]、[[风险|风险]]和[[不确定性|不确定性]]的性质和经济行为者。<ref>Paul Anand (1993, 1995). "Foundations of Rational Choice Under Risk". Oxford. Oxford University Press.</ref>

[[博弈论|博弈论]]建立在决策理论之上，在许多学科之间共享，尤其是[[数学|数学]]、[[经济学|经济学]]和[[哲学|哲学]]，在经济学哲学领域得到广泛讨论。<ref>[[Cristina_Bicchieri|Cristina Bicchieri]] (1993). ''Rationality and Coordination''. Cambridge. [http://www.cambridge.org/gb/knowledge/isbn/item1154149/?site_locale=en_GB Description] and chapter-preview links, pp. [https://books.google.com/books?id=4SQ4AAAAIAAJ&printsec=toc&dq=%22Rationality+and+Coordination%22&source=gbs_summary_s&cad=0 v-vi]. Game-theory [https://books.google.com/books?id=4SQ4AAAAIAAJ&printsec=toc&dq=#v=onepage&q=game&f=false links].</ref>

===伦理学与正义论===
{{main|补偿性正义}}
经济系统的伦理学处理诸如如何正确（公正、公平）地保留或分配经济商品等问题。“伦理学和经济学”将[[伦理学|伦理学]]与[[福利经济学|福利经济学]]联系起来。<ref>For example:
* [[Amartya_K._Sen|Amartya K. Sen]] (1970 [1984]). ''Collective Choice and Social Welfare''. Elsevier.
* [[Daniel_M._Hausman|Daniel M. Hausman]] and Michael S. McPherson (1993).  "Taking Ethics Seriously: Economics and Contemporary Moral Philosophy", ''Journal of Economic Literature'', 31(2), pp. [http://www.colorado.edu/economics/morey/4999Ethics/ethicsandmoralphilosphy/HausmanMcPherson1993_Edward.pdf 671–731].
* _____ ([1994] 2005), 2nd Ed. ''Economic Analysis and Moral Philosophy''. Cambridge University Press.
* [[Hal_R._Varian|Hal R. Varian]] (1975).  "Distributive Justice, Welfare Economics, and the Theory of Fairness", ''Philosophy & Public Affairs'' 4(3), pp. 223–247. {{JSTOR|2265084}}</ref><ref>Amartya Sen (1987). ''On Ethics and Economics'', Blackwell.</ref>

道德和正义以不同的方式重叠。当研究基本原理时，其方法被认为更具哲学性——例如，[[约翰·罗尔斯|罗尔斯]]的《[[正义论|正义论]]》（1971）<ref>[[Amartya_Sen|Amartya Sen]] (1990). "Justice: Means versus Freedoms," ''Philosophy & Public Affairs'', 19(2), pp. [https://www.jstor.org/pss/2265406 111]-121.</ref>和[[羅伯特·諾齊克|诺齐克]]的《[[無政府、國家與烏托邦|無政府、國家與烏托邦]]》（1974）。<ref>For example:
* [[Richard_Posner|Richard Posner]] (1981). ''The Economics of Justice''. [http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog/POSECO.html Description] and chapter links, pp. [https://books.google.com/books?id=CKEN0F07ChUC&dq=%22economic+analysis+of+law%22+posner&printsec=frontcover&source=bl&ots=GS4jOgg4as&sig=ESu3j8utNT12CSzI_cMU8DMJhYI&hl=en&ei=t54YSrO4K9DHtgfq_72BDQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8#PPR11,M1 xi-xiii].
* David A. Hoffman and Michael P. O'Shea (2002). "Can Law and Economics Be Both Practical and Principled?" ''Alabama Law Review'',  53(2), pp.  [http://works.bepress.com/hoffman/4/ 335–420].</ref>

[[功利主义|功利主义]]作为一种伦理方法论，其渊源与[[经济学史|现代经济思想的兴起]]密不可分。今天，功利主义作为众多方法之一在[[應用倫理學|应用伦理学]]中传播开来。应用伦理学中也有非功利主义方法——例如基于权利的[[义务论|义务论]](deontological)方法。

许多[[政治意识形态|政治意识形态]]是对经济制度伦理反思的直接产物。[[马克思|马克思]]是一位哲学家，他最著名的著作《资本论》是关于经济哲学的。

===非主流经济学===
{{main|异端经济学}}
从值得注意但通常代表性不足的群体的角度来看，经济学的基础和假设受到质疑。例如：

* [[奥地利经济学派|奥地利经济学派]]或称[[人類行為學|人类行为学]]：自觉反对以数学建模和假设检验来验证[[新古典經濟學派|新古典经济学]]。<ref>[https://mises.org/about-mises/what-is-the-mises-Institute What Is the Mises Institute? Mission Statement].</ref><ref>[https://mises.org/library/praxeology-methodology-austrian-economics Praxeology: The Methodology of Austrian Economics Praxeology: The Methodology of Austrian Economics]. Murray N. Rothbard (1976)</ref>
* 经济学的跨文化视角和[[经济人类学|经济人类学]]：一个例子是佛教启发的[[不丹|不丹]]“幸福GDP”概念。[[阿马蒂亚·库马尔·森|阿马蒂亚·库马尔·森]]是著名的将跨文化现象融入经济思维的倡导者。<ref>Amartya Sen (2008). [http://www.pyinnya.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/culture-and-development.pdf "Culture and Development."] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005211313/http://www.pyinnya.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/culture-and-development.pdf |date=2011-10-05 }}</ref>
* 女性主义经济学观点或[[女性主义经济学|女性主义经济学]]。<ref>For example: Drucilla Barker & Edith Kuiper eds., {{cite book |year=2003 |title=Towards a feminist philosophy of economics |publisher=Routledge |isbn=0-415-28388-4  }}</ref>

